---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - implicit.ai" description="Terms of Service for implicit.ai pilot engagements">
  <Nav />
  <main class="legal container">
    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="legal__updated">Last updated: April 2026</p>

    <section>
      <h2>1. Scope of Service</h2>
      <p>
        These Terms of Service govern access to and use of implicit.ai's AI-powered innovation intelligence platform and
        any associated pilot engagement services (collectively, the "Service"), provided by implicit.ai ("we", "us",
        "our") to the customer ("you", "Client").
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>2. Pilot Terms</h2>
      <p>
        Pilot engagements are time-limited, scoped programmes designed to demonstrate the value of the Service within
        your organisation. The scope, duration, and deliverables of each pilot will be agreed in writing prior to
        commencement. No ongoing commitment is implied by participation in a pilot.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>3. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>
        All intellectual property rights in the Service - including underlying AI models, software, and methodologies -
        remain exclusively with implicit.ai. You retain ownership of all data and content you provide. By using the
        Service, you grant us a limited, non-exclusive licence to process your data solely for the purpose of delivering
        the Service.
      </p>
      <p>
        Insights, maps, and reports generated through the Service are provided to you under a non-exclusive licence for
        your internal business use only.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>4. Liability</h2>
      <p>
        The Service is provided on an "as is" basis. To the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, we exclude all
        warranties, express or implied. We shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages
        arising from your use of the Service.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our total liability to you in connection with any claim shall not exceed the amounts paid by you in the three
        months preceding the claim.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>5. Termination</h2>
      <p>
        Either party may terminate a pilot engagement by providing 7 days' written notice. We reserve the right to
        suspend or terminate access immediately in the event of material breach of these Terms.
      </p>
      <p>
        On termination, we will provide a data export upon request within 30 days, after which your data will be
        securely deleted.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>6. Governing Law</h2>
      <p>
        These Terms are governed by the laws of the Federal Republic of Germany. The courts of [City], Germany shall
        have exclusive jurisdiction over any disputes arising from these Terms.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>7. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For any questions regarding these Terms, please contact us at:
        <a href="mailto:legal@implicit.ai">legal@implicit.ai</a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal {
    padding: var(--space-16) var(--space-4);
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .legal h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .legal__updated {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
  }

  .legal section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .legal h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .legal p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .legal a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
